{"tid":1652720,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【討論post】幫中國火上加油","createTime":"2019-10-13T18:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T19:31:54.000Z","uid":209850,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2248fb23dadd3ffd25d44534479c4d568400a1f0","tid":1652720,"uid":209850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iUicaAA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiUicaAA.jpg&h=0da65c0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRt31Hg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqRt31Hg.jpg&h=e59912fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講左幾個月將革命輸出番支那成效都係唔多明顯<br />\n<br />\n既然係咁，唯有玩另一樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班支那人咁愛國成日屌鳩我地港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又話中國領土一點都不能少<br />\n咁作為連登仔就一於借力打力，利用班支那既愛國心向俄國斯開火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講番比啲支那人知中國領土比俄羅斯吞併左幾多，我地<span style=\"color: red;\">要幫國家奪回領土</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試下打着紅旗反紅旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攞正牌幫支共增添麻煩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要搞砸支共先要令佢國際間孤立佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一黎可以令支共冇左俄仔呢個重要靠山<br />\n二黎班五毛唔得閒搞我地 要應付國內輿論<br />\n<br />\n真係搞得成要支共人民同俄羅斯反面，真係諗起都興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb9be8a4f0ae8358abd0fb566c6ab985922c7c5","tid":1652720,"uid":209850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:48:37.000Z","msg":"自推*10"},{"pid":"eeaeddfbc05459298d26d578c3ed877c8cb7226b","tid":1652720,"uid":209850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"